{
  "texts": [
    "This paper provides a practical overview of how ML has been used for scanpath analysis in passive gaze-based applications.",
    "Our contribution lies in reporting and summarizing findings from 77 publications between 2012 and 2022.",
    "We begin by examining the different research domains and passive gaze-based learning tasks to see the current trends in the field.",
    "Afterwards, we structure our ML findings in the order of a general ML workflow based on those from Amershi et al.",
    "(2019) and Souza et al. (2022)."
  ]
}